Suicidal Thoughts?

If you're thinking about suicide or experiencing a mental health crisis, please call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline immediately at 1-800-273-8255 or text HOME to 741741 to reach the Crisis Text Line.

These services are free, confidential, and available 24/7. You don't have to face depression alone.
